title: Tartu Rose
text:
Tartu Rose () is an <a href="apple">apple</a> <a href="cultivar">cultivar</a> from <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>.
At first it was thought to be an original cultivar and therefore named with its own name. Later, a strong similarity to the American '<a href="Wealthy%20%28apple%29">Wealthy</a>' cultivar was discovered.
